<br>
A courier has arrived from the Ocean of Tears bringing most extraordinary news! The Oracle had a vision in which Veeshan spoke to him. The mighty god demanded that a carnival held to his name should be a celebration of craft, art and beauty. Therefore we humbly abide to his will and announce the following.<br>
<br>
We have decided to host not one, not two, but at least four contests! After all do not want to risk offending Veeshan...<br>
<br>
A contest for all poets! All who enter will be asked to show their talent in just four verses (no more than 60 words). An independent jury will pick the winner. We have consulted the seers and they claim that poems describing any aspects of the life on Norrath (or Luclin) would please Veeshan most.<br>
<br>
A fashion pageant! The best dressed Norrathian will be selected from all participants by our judges.<br>
<br>
A jesters competition! All entrants will have the stage for two minutes, the audience will pick the winner! We were warned by the leaders of the bard's guild that Veeshan does not tolerate vulgar jokes of the kind the Ry'Gorr seem to like.<br>
<br>
A riddle contest! Nine riddles will be presented, the one to guess the most will walk away with the prize.<br>
<br>
A purse containing no less than a thousand platinum coins will be awarded to every winner. Most likely the prizes will be increased, this will be announced soon. <br>
<br>
If you want to enter any of those competitions, please register. You may leave a post below, or contact Celo or Skafid. There will be a limit of entrants to all of the events.  <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm39.showPrevMessage?topicID=407.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm39.showNextMessage?topicID=407.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a self href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm39.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=407.topic&index=1><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/classic/addReply.jpg border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"><a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm39.threadControl?topicID=407.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/professional/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands</a><br> <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm39.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=407.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/ultimate/subscribe.gif width=20 height=20 border=0 alt="Click to receive email notification of replies"> Click to receive email notification of replies</a> <br>  <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm39.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=407.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/ultimate/unsubscribe.gif width=20 height=20 border=0 alt="Click to stop receiving email notification of replies"> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies</a> <br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub94.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum method=post><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="1"><tr><td><b>jump to:</b><select name=forumName><option value="fi